lb.name: lb
lb.description: This MIB file contains definitions of managed objects for the LB module.

lbShowGlobalTable.name: lbShowGlobalTable
lbShowGlobalTable.description: General configuration and status of all of the virtual balancers configured on the router.

lbShowGlobalEntry.name: lbShowGlobalEntry
lbShowGlobalEntry.description: An entry in the global table.

lbGlobalIndex.name: lbGlobalIndex
lbGlobalIndex.description: The index for the global table.

lbAffinityTimeOut.name: lbAffinityTimeOut
lbAffinityTimeOut.description: The length of time in seconds that a resource can be associated to a source IP address or Cookie after the connection has been closed.

lbOrphanTimeOut.name: lbOrphanTimeOut
lbOrphanTimeOut.description: The length of time in seconds that a connection can exist without having any data traversing it, before being declared an orphan and closed by the router.

lbCriticalRst.name: lbCriticalRst
lbCriticalRst.description: The ratio of total messages received from a resource that can be TCP RST messages represented as a percentage.

lbTotalResources.name: lbTotalResources
lbTotalResources.description: The total number of resources configured on the router.

lbTotalResPools.name: lbTotalResPools
lbTotalResPools.description: The total number of resource pools configured on the router.

lbTotalVirtBals.name: lbTotalVirtBals
lbTotalVirtBals.description: The total number of virtual balancers configured on the router.

lbCurrentConnections.name: lbCurrentConnections
lbCurrentConnections.description: Displays the current total number of connections to all resources in every resource pool on the router.

lbShowResTable.name: lbShowResTable
lbShowResTable.description: A list about the general information about for a given resource.

lbShowResEntry.name: lbShowResEntry
lbShowResEntry.description: An entry in the resource table.

lbResIndex.name: lbResIndex
lbResIndex.description: The index for the resource table.

lbResIp.name: lbResIp
lbResIp.description: The IP address that a virtual balancer uses to accesses the resource.

lbResPort.name: lbResPort
lbResPort.description: The port that the service that the resource offer is accessed on.

lbResState.name: lbResState
lbResState.description: The current state of the resource, either UP, DOWN, or CLOSING.

lbResWeight.name: lbResWeight
lbResWeight.description: The weight that the virtual balancer will apply to the resource when selecting resources to try a connection to from a resource pool using either the WEIGHTEDLEASTCONNECT or WEIGHTEDLOTTERY selection algorithms.

lbResTotalConnections.name: lbResTotalConnections
lbResTotalConnections.description: The total number of successful connections that have been made to this resource while it has been in the UP state.

lbResCurrentConnections.name: lbResCurrentConnections
lbResCurrentConnections.description: The total number of connections currently made to the resource.

lbShowResPoolTable.name: lbShowResPoolTable
lbShowResPoolTable.description: A list about the general information about for a given resource pool.

lbShowResPoolEntry.name: lbShowResPoolEntry
lbShowResPoolEntry.description: An entry in the resource pool table.

lbResPoolIndex.name: lbResPoolIndex
lbResPoolIndex.description: The index for the resource pool table.

lbResPoolResourceIndex.name: lbResPoolResourceIndex
lbResPoolResourceIndex.description: The index for the resource table.

lbResPool.name: lbResPool
lbResPool.description: The name of the resource pool.

lbResPoolSelectionAlg.name: lbResPoolSelectionAlg
lbResPoolSelectionAlg.description: The selection algorithm that ius employed by this resource pool when a resource has been selected for a connection. The options are ROUNDROBIN, WEIGHTEDLEASTCONNECT, WEIGHTEDLOTTERY and FASTESTRESPONSE.

lbResPoolFailOnLast.name: lbResPoolFailOnLast
lbResPoolFailOnLast.description: Indicates whether or not the resource pool will fail a resource if it is the last resource in the resource pool.

lbResPoolTotalConnections.name: lbResPoolTotalConnections
lbResPoolTotalConnections.description: The total number of successful connections that have been made to the resources in the resource pool over the lifetime of the resource pool.

lbResPoolResources.name: lbResPoolResources
lbResPoolResources.description: The name of the resource that is currently allocated to the resource pool.

lbShowVirtBalTable.name: lbShowVirtBalTable
lbShowVirtBalTable.description: A list about the general information about for a given virtual balancer.

lbShowVirtBalEntry.name: lbShowVirtBalEntry
lbShowVirtBalEntry.description: An entry in the virtual balancer table.

lbVirtBalIndex.name: lbVirtBalIndex
lbVirtBalIndex.description: The index for the virtual balancer table.

lbVirtBal.name: lbVirtBal
lbVirtBal.description: The name of the virtual balancer.

lbVirtBalPublicIp.name: lbVirtBalPublicIp
lbVirtBalPublicIp.description: The IP address on which the virtual balancer will receive requests for the service provided by the resource pool associated with it.

lbVirtBalPublicPort.name: lbVirtBalPublicPort
lbVirtBalPublicPort.description: The port on which the virtual balancer will receive requests for the service provided by the resource pool associated with it.

lbVirtBalState.name: lbVirtBalState
lbVirtBalState.description: The current state of the virtual balancer, can either be UP, CLOSING, or DOWN.

lbVirtBalResPool.name: lbVirtBalResPool
lbVirtBalResPool.description: The name of the resource pool that is associated with the virtual balancer.

lbVirtBalType.name: lbVirtBalType
lbVirtBalType.description: The type of load balancer that this virtual balancer currently is, can be either TCP, HTTP, or ROUTE.

lbVirtBalTotalConnections.name: lbVirtBalTotalConnections
lbVirtBalTotalConnections.description: The total number of stateful connections currently running through this virtual balancer.

lbVirtBalAffinity.name: lbVirtBalAffinity
lbVirtBalAffinity.description: Indicates whether or not entries will be made in a virtual balancers' affinity table for each stateful connection to a resource in its' resource pool (TCP and ROUTE type) or for cookies received from clients (HTTP type).

lbVirtBalHttpErrorCode.name: lbVirtBalHttpErrorCode
lbVirtBalHttpErrorCode.description: A list of the HTTP server error status code added.

lbShowAffTable.name: lbShowAffTable
lbShowAffTable.description: A list of affinity tables for all configured virtual balancers on the router.

lbShowAffEntry.name: lbShowAffEntry
lbShowAffEntry.description: An entry in the affinity table.

lbAffIndex.name: lbAffIndex
lbAffIndex.description: The index for the affinity table.

lbAffVirtBal.name: lbAffVirtBal
lbAffVirtBal.description: The name of the virtual balancer whose affinity table is being displayed.

lbAffClientIp.name: lbAffClientIp
lbAffClientIp.description: The IP address that has affinity to the given resource.

lbAffCookie.name: lbAffCookie
lbAffCookie.description: The cookie that has affinity to the given resource.

lbAffResource.name: lbAffResource
lbAffResource.description: The name of the resource that the Client IP/Cookie has an affinity for.

lbAffExpiry.name: lbAffExpiry
lbAffExpiry.description: The amount of seconds left before this entry expires, and is removed from the affinity table.

lbShowConTable.name: lbShowConTable
lbShowConTable.description: A list about all of the TCP connections currently open to a given virtual balancer.

lbShowConEntry.name: lbShowConEntry
lbShowConEntry.description: An entry in the connections table.

lbConIndex.name: lbConIndex
lbConIndex.description: The index for the connections table.

lbConVirtBal.name: lbConVirtBal
lbConVirtBal.description: The name of the virtual balancer the listed connections are to.

lbConClientIp.name: lbConClientIp
lbConClientIp.description: The IP address of that originated the connection.

lbConPort.name: lbConPort
lbConPort.description: The port on the originating system that represents the other end of the connection.

lbConResource.name: lbConResource
lbConResource.description: The name of the resource that the connection has been made to.
